## Sheet 2: Scoring Matrix

### Scoring Methodology

| Aspect | Weight | Us | Comp 1 | Comp 2 | Comp 3 |
|--------|--------|----|----- ---|--------|--------|
| Feature Coverage | 30% | [Score] | [Score] | [Score] | [Score] |
| Implementation Quality | 25% | [Score] | [Score] | [Score] | [Score] |
| User Satisfaction | 20% | [Score] | [Score] | [Score] | [Score] |
| Performance | 15% | [Score] | [Score] | [Score] | [Score] |
| Ease of Use | 10% | [Score] | [Score] | [Score] | [Score] |
| **Total** | 100% | [Formula] | [Formula] | [Formula] | [Formula] |

### Calculation Formulas

```
Total Score = Σ (Aspect Score × Weight)

Feature Coverage = (Features Have / Total Features) × 100
Implementation Quality = Average quality rating (1-5)
User Satisfaction = Average from reviews (1-5)
```

